<h2 class="bold font-l">Ice Age Who's up for Round 2?!</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
After after the animals all go hurtling through an Ice slide maze and slam into a wall, Diego punches the air and eagerly asks who wants to go do it again. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/WasntThatFun" class='trope-example-link'>Wasn't That Fun?</a></p>
